# Help Display Template
#
# This template generates the help content for gateway commands.
# Placeholders use {{placeholder}} syntax and are replaced at generation time.
#
# Designed for ASCII box display (Kleene-style) with visual separators.

```
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
{{PLUGIN_TITLE}} - {{plugin_description}}
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

{{#skill_sections}}
{{section_name}}
{{#skills}}
  /{{plugin_name}} {{skill_command}}{{padding}}{{skill_description}}
{{/skills}}

{{/skill_sections}}
RUNTIME FLAGS
  --verbose, -v    Show all node details and condition evaluations
  --quiet, -q      Only user prompts and final result
  --terse          Batch summaries only
  --debug          Full state dumps
  --log-level=X    Set logging (error/warn/info/debug/trace)
  --no-log         Disable logging

HELP
  /{{plugin_name}} --help            This help screen
  /{{plugin_name}} help [skill]      Help for specific skill
  /{{plugin_name}} help flags        Explain runtime flags

EXAMPLES
{{#examples}}
  {{command}}
{{/examples}}

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
```

---

## Template Variables

| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `{{PLUGIN_TITLE}}` | Plugin name in uppercase | `HIIVMIND-BLUEPRINT` |
| `{{plugin_name}}` | Plugin name for commands | `hiivmind-blueprint` |
| `{{plugin_description}}` | Short description | `Workflow Conversion System` |
| `{{skill_sections}}` | Array of skill category sections | See below |
| `{{examples}}` | Array of example commands | See below |

### Skill Sections Structure

```yaml
skill_sections:
  - section_name: "CONVERSION PIPELINE"
    skills:
      - skill_command: "init"
        padding: "              "  # Align descriptions
        skill_description: "Set up plugin for workflows"
      - skill_command: "discover"
        padding: "          "
        skill_description: "Find skills to convert"
```

### Examples Structure

```yaml
examples:
  - command: "/hiivmind-blueprint init ../my-plugin"
  - command: "/hiivmind-blueprint analyze my-skill"
```

