## Skill-Specific Help Template

For individual skill help (`show_skill_help_*`), use this structure:

```markdown
## {{plugin_name}}-{{skill_id}}

**Purpose:** {{skill_purpose}}

**Usage:**
\`\`\`
/{{plugin_name}} {{skill_command}} [args]
/{{plugin_name}} {{skill_command}} --verbose
\`\`\`

**What it does:**
{{#steps}}
{{step_number}}. {{step_description}}
{{/steps}}

**Examples:**
\`\`\`
{{#skill_examples}}
{{example}}
{{/skill_examples}}
\`\`\`
```

